2:[["$","$L7",null,{"headerBgImage":"/images/articles/news-ai-workflow.jpg"}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-page news-article-page","style":{"padding":0},"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","style":{"padding":"0 24px"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"blog-entry-category","children":"20 March 2026"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"Google 发布 Android 侧载应用新政策"}],["$","div",null,{"dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<h3>新政策内容</h3>\n<p>Google 宣布了 Android 系统上侧载应用的新验证流程。用户从非 Play Store 渠道安装应用时，需要经过更严格的身份验证和安全检查。</p>\n\n<h3>主要变化</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>首次侧载需要验证身份</li>\n<li>每次安装应用都需要用户确认</li>\n<li>增加了恶意软件检测提醒</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>用户反应</h3>\n<p>这一政策引发了广泛讨论。部分用户认为这是为了提高安全性，但也有人担心这会影响 Android 的开放性。</p>\n\n<h3>专家观点</h3>\n<p>安全专家表示，在移动端面临越来越多恶意软件的背景下，Google 的这一举措是合理的。但需要平衡安全性与用户体验。</p>"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"share-links","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Twitter","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-twitter"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"LinkedIn","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-linkedin-in"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Facebook","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-facebook-f"}]}]]}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-light pt-4 pb-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h3",null,{"style":{"marginBottom":"24px","fontSize":"18px","fontWeight":700},"children":"其他新闻"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"posts-grid","children":[["$","div","astral-join-openai",{"className":"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4 blog-item","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"card h-100","children":["$","$L8",null,{"href":"/posts/astral-join-openai","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"position-relative","children":["$","img",null,{"src":"/images/articles/news-ai-robot.jpg","className":"blog-image","alt":"Astral 团队加入 OpenAI：Python 工具作者的下一站"}]